<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Karl Teufel</head><p>Der Rat teilt mit, dass Teufels verstorbener Bruder Konrad nach Aussage der Witwe und des Vormunds kaum Vermögen, sondern meist Schulden hinterlassen hat; in seinem Testament hat Konrad Teufel keine Schulden bei Karl Teufel erwähnt.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_250" id="124v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_250_r2l1">Karl Tewfel / </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_250_r2l2"><expan>Lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan> Karl / Als du vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> haſt von <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> Tewfels deins </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_250_r2l3"><expan>brüd<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>ſelıge<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd der habe die er <expan>gelaſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> hat / . Darvmb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_250_r2l5"> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir 
<del rend="strikethrough">ſein vormünde </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_250_line_1576582364756_3246">ſein wirtin vnd ſein vormünd beſant </ab></add> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_250_line_1576582367996_3251">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex></expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_250_r2l6">
<del rend="strikethrough">beſant / vnd die <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vns geſagt / wie er ein geſchefte getan </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_250_r2l7">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>daryn<ex>n</ex>e</expan> er ſie cʒe vormünden geſacʒt hab </del> / . vnd ſie <expan>ſprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_250_r2l8">er vaſt ſchulde / vnd nicht vil v̈brigs gelaſſen hab / 
<add><ab facs="#facs_250_r1l2">vnd er hab auch </ab><ab facs="#facs_250_r1l3">ein geſcheft </ab><ab facs="#facs_250_r1l4">getan / <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> dem </ab><ab facs="#facs_250_r1l5">das er <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> ge </ab><ab facs="#facs_250_r1l6">laſſen hab / </ab><ab facs="#facs_250_r1l7">vnd ſie <expan>wiſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_250_r1l8"><expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>keine<ex>m</ex></expan> handel </ab><ab facs="#facs_250_r1l9">noch ſchulden </ab><ab facs="#facs_250_r1l10">von deinen <expan>vvege<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab></add> Doch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_250_r2l9">dewcht dich daʒ du <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒü 
<del rend="strikethrough">den <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan></del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_250_line_1576582379230_3264">Jn </ab></add> <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>B<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_250_r2l10"><expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> ıht <expan>cʒeſprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> heſt / <expan>Dar<ex>vmb</ex></expan> <expan>vvölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_250_r2l11">dir <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>deine<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>ſcheimbot<ex>en</ex></expan> mit <expan>deine<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalt <expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>cʒoge<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_250_r2l12"><expan>ſlewnig<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> <expan>helff<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>wen<ex>n</ex></expan> wir des ermant <expan>w<ex>er</ex>d<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_250_r2l13">ſo <expan>dieſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>e</expan> <expan>B<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒü den du <expan>cʒeſprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> haſt anheim </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_250_r2l14">ſind / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_250" id="124v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Karl Tewfel </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> Karl, als du uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hast von
                                <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> Tewfels, deins
                            <expan>brüd<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, <expan>selige<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> und der habe, die er
                                <expan>gelasse<ex>n</ex></expan> hat, darumb
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <add>sein wirtin und sein vormünd
                            besant</add> und sie <expan>sprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz er vast
                        schulde und nicht vil übrigs gelassen hab, <add>und er hab auch ein gescheft
                            getan <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> dem, das er
                                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> ge lassen hab, und sie
                                    <expan>wisse<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>keine<ex>m</ex></expan> handel noch schulden von deinen
                                    <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan></add>. Doch dewcht dich, daz du
                                <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> czü <add>in</add>
<expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> iht
                                <expan>czesprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hest,
                            <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir dir <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>deine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>scheimbot<ex>en</ex></expan> mit <expan>deine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalt
                            <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czoge<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>slewnig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>
<expan>helff<ex>en,</ex></expan>
<expan>wen<ex>n</ex></expan> wir des ermant
                            <expan>w<ex>er</ex>d<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, so
                            <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>e</expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex></expan>, czü den du <expan>cze
                                sprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hast, anheim sind.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
